n><hr size=1> Well, I never thought <a href=http://noows.com/showthread.php?s=&threadid=3063&perpage=15&pagenumber=1>this</a> would happen.  Seems Furor, the guildleader of Fires of Heaven, decided to hang it all up.<br>
<br>
I can't really make some profound statement, since I never knew the guy, but you have to admit what FoH has done is pretty damned impressive.<br>
<br>
Just something I think some people might want to know. <p>--------------------<BR>Hizuka<BR>Swifttail of the 49th Rung<BR>Initiate of the Lost Circle<BR>Innoruuk Server<BR><BR>In Void there is good but no evil.  Wisdom exists, logic exists, the Way exists, mind is empty.<BR><i>Miyamoto Musashi, The Book of Five Rings</i></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/usabatiniscratch.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Sabatini Scratch</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(8/21/01 10:15:52 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehouseretirementwing.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=551.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.blackarcana.com/anarchy/scratchsm.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Furor Leaves EQ</span><hr size=1> Well since my impressions of him stem fully from his few visits here, I can't say I'll miss him all that much. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/unotwen.showPublicProfile?language=EN>notwen</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Safehouse Supporter</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(8/21/01 10:44:13 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehouseretirementwing.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=551.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Furor Leaves EQ</span><hr size=1> 
Well, can't say I ever had any love for the guy, especially as Sab says, after his visits here.  Still... he says some things I totally sympathize with in his goodbye message.  Particularly the sentiments about EQ and our experiences in it being more than a game... and how some might view it as pathetic, but it's not like they have picture perfect &quot;OMG amazing&quot; lives anyway.  Of course, heh, he says it in a way *I'd* probably never say it, but that's Furor I guess. <p>Notwen Gif<br>
<b>55</b> Rogue on Fennin Ro<br> 
House of Kindred<br>
</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/bthesafehouse.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=gannab>Gannab</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(8/21/01 11:21:13 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehouseretirementwing.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=551.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Furor Leaves EQ</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><i> ignorant young rogue wonders what came of the few visits of Furor at the Safehouse</i><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--> <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ufiae.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Fiae</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC=http://www.evercrack.net/photo/tinyassfiae.gif BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Rogue News Hound</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(8/21/01 2:27:44 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehouseretirementwing.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=551.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.evercrack.net/photo/tinyassfiae.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Furor Leaves EQ</span><hr size=1> Furor is crass, that's the nicest way you can put it and be within the language filter. Furor knows this, it's not a surprise, but alot of people weren't all that pleased with his attitude. <br>
