</p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ufiae.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Fiae</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC=http://www.evercrack.net/photo/tinyassfiae.gif BORDER=0> at: 8/21/01 2:36:14 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ushikakuthegorotsuki.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Shikaku the Gorotsuki</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(8/21/01 7:32:10 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehouseretirementwing.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=551.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Furor Leaves EQ</span><hr size=1> The guy may of been a real jerk... but he also could be pretty cool(Or atleast I heard he could...). He ran a great guild... but a guild leader doesnt make the guild..he just promotes people to officer status. Most great guilds have great members...who plan great raids. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uradient.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Radient</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(8/28/01 12:39:18 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehouseretirementwing.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=551.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> You, Shikaku...</span><hr size=1> are a fool <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  or at least ridiculously ignorant to think that all a guildleader does is promote people to officer status. I dont wanna turn this into some gay rant tho, so I'll close with this..<br>
<br>
A legend moves on, he did more for MMO's than most could ever know. He sure as @#%$ isnt reading this, but hey, what the hell...good luck in RL Alex<br>
<br>
rad<br>
OOP <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/ushikakuthegorotsuki.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Shikaku the Gorotsuki</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(8/28/01 4:45:33 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehouseretirementwing.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=551.topic&index=7>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: You, Shikaku...</span><hr size=1> Rad, you'd be amazed how many guild leaders just do that. It's very few who are extremely active, and he may of been one of them. But yeah, both he and his guild contributed amazing things to EQ. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uaraxasxev.showPublicProfile?language=EN>araxas xev</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(8/28/01 10:03:08 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehouseretirementwing.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=551.topic&index=8>Reply</a>    <br>Community Supporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Furor Leaves EQ</span><hr size=1> Shikaku, what level is your guild?<br>
<br>
I can guarantee you that every guild at the top of the game (not just the FoH/Afterlives, but the top 2 or 3 guilds on each server) has a strong leader to get there. Whether it's the actual guild leader or some officer may vary, but just having a bunch of lvl 58+ players doesn't make a guild. <br>
<br>
20 high level players organized by a strong leader &gt; 40 high level players with no stong leadership.<br>
<br>
If you're sentiment is &quot;guild leaders usually don't do anything but promote officers&quot; I'd suggest levelling up some so you can experience what an unorganized high level raid is like relative to an organized one. If you're already high level and still think this, go find a better guild.  <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table><table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehouseretirementwing.showPrevMessage?topicID=551.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehouseretirementwing.showNextMessage?topicID=551.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehouseretirementwing.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=551.topic&index=8><img src=http://www.thesafehouse.org/images/reply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehouseretirementwing.emailToFriend?topicID=551.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehouseretirementwing.threadControl?topicID=551.topic><img src=http://www.thesafehouse.org/images/dagger.jpg border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands (Moderator only)</a><br> <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehouseretirementwing.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=551.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehouseretirementwing.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=551.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub35.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><sel